title: „Neptūno“ moterų klubas dar metams pratęsė sutartį su Sinickaite
description: Sezono pabaigos nelaukęs Klaipėdos „Neptūnas-Amberton“ pradėjo lipdyti pamatus artėjantiems metams. Uostamiesčio klubas pratęsė sutartį su viena pagrindinių komandos žaidėjų Brigita Sinickaite. „Neptūno-Amberton“ gretose 24-erių šiaulietė rungtyniauja nuo 2022 m. ir jai tai bus ketvirtasis sezonas iš eilės. „Pagrindinės priežastys likti Klaipėdoje buvo dėl parodyto didelio pasitikėjimo, noro išlaikyti mane iš vadovybės pusės bei gerų suteiktų sąlygų, – sprendimą pratęsti sutartį aiškino Sinickaitė. – „Neptūnas“ tapo ta vieta, kurioje pamilau krepšinį iš naujo ir čia žaisdama jaučiuosi labai gerai.“ Vasario mėnesį vykusiame Europos čempionato atrankos lange atakuojanti gynėja padėjo Lietuvos moterų krepšinio rinktinei po 10 metų pertraukos grįžti į Senojo žemyno pirmenybes. 173 cm ūgio krepšininkė šį „SMART WAY MLKL“ sezoną per 24 minutes fiksuoja 9,4 taško, 3,4 atkovoto ir 1,7 perimto kamuolio, 4,1 rezultatyvaus perdavimo bei 10,6 naudingumo balo. Baltijos čempionato 2024-25 m. sezone Sinickaitė per 15 susitikimų vidutiniškai renka po 6,1 taško, 3,7 sugriebto ir 1,4 perimto kamuolio, 4,1 rezultatyvaus perdavimo bei 8,8 efektyvumo balo. Praėjusį sezoną krepšininkė su uostamiesčio klubu iškovojo Karalienės taurę ir pasipuošė „BioSil-Baltijos lygos“ bei „SMART WAY MLKL“ bronzos medaliais. Šiemet gynėja tapo Karalienės taurės vicečempione.

description_translated: After not waiting for the end of the season, Klaipeda Neptune-Agerton began to launch the foundations for the upcoming year. The Port City Club extended the contract with one of the team's main players Brigita Sinickaite. The 24-year-old Šiauliai has been competing since 2022 in the Neptune-Amberton ranks. And for her, it will be the fourth season in a row. "The main reasons to stay in Klaipeda were due to the great confidence shown, the desire to maintain me from the management side and the good conditions," Sinickaite explained the decision to extend the contract. title: Knygos apie „Nord Stream“ autorius: Vokietija atmerktomis akimis finansavo Putino karą
description: Dujotiekiai „Nord Stream“ niekada nebuvo vien ekonominis projektas – tai buvo Vladimiro Putino geopolitinis galios įrankis. Vamzdžiais tekančiomis gana pigiomis dujomis Kremlius prisirišo Vokietiją, kuri milijardus eurų kasmet pumpavo į Rusijos kišenę, iš kurios finansuojamas karas Ukrainoje. Du Vokietijos žurnalistai – Steffenas Dobbertas ir Ulrichas Thiele – tai detaliai chronologiškai aprašo savo naujoje knygoje „Nord Stream. Kaip Vokietija moka už Putino karą“. Jiedu atskleidžia, kaip Vokietijos politikai ir institucijos tapo naudingais idiotais ir Kremliaus bendrininkais.
title_translated: Author of a book on Nord Stream: Germany funded the Putin War with his eyes closed
description_translated: The Nord Stream pipelines have never been an economic project - it was Vladimir Putin's geopolitical power tool. The Kremlin was attached to Germany with a rather cheap gas, which pumped billions of euros every year into a Russian pocket, funded by a war in Ukraine. Two German journalists - Steffen Dobbert and Ulrich Thiele - are chronologically described in their new book, Nord Stream. How Germany pay for Putin's War. title: Kai sužino apie šią ligą, dažnai jau būna vėlu: įvardijo požymius, kad inkstai „spaudžia stabdį“

Laurynas Rimševičius išskyrė kelias esmines priežastis.
title_translated: When you find out about this disease, it is often too late: have identified the signs that the kidneys are "pressing the brake"

Laurynas Rimševičius highlighted several major reasons.

title: Dėl nykstančių pelkių kyla grėsmė paukščiams ir augalams – dalis jau yra sunaikinta
description: Lietuvoje kritiškai nyksta pelkės. Mokslininkai sako, kad tai kelia didžiulę grėsmę nykstančioms gyvūnų ir augalų rūšims, o taip pat ir visai ekosistemai. Mokslininkų skaičiavimais, beveik 40 procentų visų Lietuvos pelkių jau yra sunaikinta dėl ūkininkystės. Ekologai kreipiasi į valdžios atstovus ir prašo, kad šie skatintų ūkininkus saugoti pelkes, rinktųsi aplinkai draugiškesnius ūkininkavimo metodus.
title_translated: The endangered swamps are threatened by birds and plants - part is already destroyed
description_translated: The wetlands are critically disappearing in Lithuania. Scientists say this is a major threat to endangered animal and plant species, as well as the entire ecosystem. According to scientists, almost 40 percent of all Lithuanian wetlands have already been destroyed due to farming. Ecologists turn to government representatives and ask them to encourage farmers to protect wetlands and to choose environmentally friendly farming methods.

title: Dėl ligos vos galėjusi paeiti 64-erių vilnietė žengs podiumu: nereikia bijoti pensijos
description: Vilnietė Virginija Cimermonienė, kuriai balandį sueis 65-eri, gyvenime yra patyrusi daug išbandymų – prieš 20 metų ji staiga neteko vyro, prieš keletą metų patyrė įmonės bankrotą ir susirgo reta sunkia liga. Dabar ji savanoriauja „Pagalbos moterims linijoje“ – kaip ji sakė LRT.lt, jaučia, kad, pati daug išgyvenusi, gali būti naudinga kitoms. Ponia Virginija ir dabar nestokoja optimizmo ir noro veikti, o kad būtų dar įdomiau, ryžosi savo jėgas išbandyti modelio darbe senjorams skirtame renginyje.
title_translated: Due to the illness, the 64-year-old from Vilnius will go to the podium: no need to be afraid of a pension
description_translated: Virginija Cimermonienė, a Vilnius resident, who is 65 in April, has experienced many challenges in her life-she suddenly lost her husband 20 years ago, suffered a company bankrupt a few years ago and had a rare serious illness. Now she volunteers for "Women in the Line" - as she said LRT.lt, she feels that, after a lot of survival, it can be useful for others. Mrs. Virginia is still not lacking in optimism and desire to act, and to make it even more interesting, she decided to try her hand at a model for seniors.

title: Atmosfera Kaune mėgavęsis Obradovičius: „Kaskart norisi čia atvykti“
description: Kauno „Žalgiris“ paskutinėse sezono Eurolygos namų rungtynėse užtrenkė duris į atkrintamąsias Belgrado „Partizan“ klubui. Šio vyr. treneris Željko Obradovičius po mačo kalbėjo apie atmosferą Nemuno saloje bei įvertino komandos sezoną. Andrea Trinchieri auklėtiniai svečius iš Serbijos ketvirtadienį sausakimšoje „Žalgirio“ arenoje įveikė 70:66. „Pirmiausia noriu pasakyti tai, kad malonumas yra būti tokioje arenoje ir atmosferoje. Tai – ypatinga ir kaskart norisi čia atvykti, – spaudos konferenciją pradėjo „Partizan“ strategas. – Noriu pasveikinti „Žalgirį“ su pergale, kurią nulėmė mažos detalės ir jie jos nusipelnė. Krepšinyje reikia būti susikoncentravus į daugelį aspektų. Antroje pusėje jie nugalėjo mus savo kamuoliais puolime ir man sunku tai suprasti, kadangi didžiąją laiko dalį žaidėme su trimis aukštaūgiais. Mūsų puolimas prieš jų keitimosi gynybą buvo labai blogas ir tai nulėmė mačą. Noriu padėkoti visiems „Partizan“ sirgaliams, kurie atvyko palaikyti komandą, jų palaikymas kasmet yra išskirtinis ir aš tai vertinu.“ Spaudos konferencija (Obradovičius kalba nuo 1:25): //www.youtube.com/embed/KIYR1rC8hrA Po šio susitikimo, likus vienam turui iki reguliariojo sezono pabaigos, „Partizan“ žengia 12-ta (16-17), „Žalgiris“ – 13-tas (15-18). Pirmojo dešimtuko riba šiuo metu nubrėžta ties 18 laimėjimų. – Po šios nesėkmės nebepretenduojate į įkrintamąsias, tad kaip įvertintumėte šį sezoną? Ar galima laikyti tai nusivylimu? – Žinoma, nusivylimas, nes tikėjau šia komanda ir jos galimybėmis būti tarp geriausių klubų. Nežaidėme gerai, turėjome problemų, bet tai nėra pasiteisinimas. Komandoje visi turi kautis, tačiau nenoriu sakyti, jog šiandien nesikovėme. – Praėjusią vasarą „Partizan“ pristatė visiškai naują sudėtį. Ar po šio sezono manote įmanoma tokiai naujai komandai pretenduoti į įkrintamąsias ar TOP8? – Sakiau tai daug kartų, kad mano noras nebuvo pakeisti visos sudėties, bet tai nutiko dėl įvairių priežasčių. Sakyčiau turėjome panašų sezoną, kaip „Žalgiris“ – kartais laimėjome ir pralaimėjome neįtikėtiniais būdais. Kalbėti apie tai anksti, nes dar žaisime namuose ir ABA lygoje. Šie dalykai yra geri diskusijai jau po sezono. Žinoma, atsakomybė yra ant mano trenerio pečių. – Prieš rungtynes pasakėte daug gerų žodžių apie Andrea Trinchieri ar galite detalizuoti, ką labiausiai jame mėgstate? – Jis puikus strategas. Suprantu, ką jis nori padaryti ir kaip jo komanda žaidžia. Jis padarė puikų darbą šį sezoną. „Lietkabelį“ stebintis Željko užstojo Trinchieri: „Sakau atvirai – „Žalgiris“ žaidžia puikų krepšinį“ – Ar galite pasakyti keletą žodžių ir apie Aleną Smailagičių? Ar po šio sezono Kaune jis yra kiek kitoks žaidėjas? – Ne, jis nėra pasikeitęs. Žinome, ką jis gali, Alenas buvo pas mus trejus metus ir linkiu jam visko kuo geriausio. title: Trinchieri – apie iššūkius su Smailagičiumi ir pirmąsyk nugalėtą Obradovičių
description: Kauno „Žalgirio“ vyriausiasis treneris Andrea Trinchieri po pergalingų paskutinių Eurolygos sezono namų rungtynių kalbėjo apie solidų gynybinį pasirodymą, Aleno Smailagičiaus bangavimą ir Eurolygos juodąjį arkliuką. Trinchieri auklėtiniai ketvirtadienį sausakimšoje arenoje 70:66 palaužė Belgrado „Partizan“, o italas įžanginėje kalboje pažymėjo komandos pokytį po pertraukos. „Labai kietos rungtynės, kur turėjome nusipelnyti kiekvieno metimo. Pirmojoje pusėje jutau, kad valgome dešrainį be garstyčių – jokio skonio, – sakė Trinchieri. – Žaidėme, bet be reikiamos įtampos, reikalingos žaidžiant su „Partizan“. Sužaidėme tragišką antrąjį kėlinį, koncentravomės tik į puolimą. Nesustabdėme Carliko Joneso nė vieno karto. Bet antrojoje pusėje žaidėme taip, kaip turėtume. Galėjo laimėti abi komandos, bet mes gerai susigynėme pabaigoje. Galiausiai nusipelnėme laimėti.“ Kauno komandai Alenas Smailagičius per 22 minutes pelnė 14 taškų (4/5 dvit., 1/1 trit., 3/4 baudų), atkovojo 4 kamuolius, atliko 1 rezultatyvų perdavimą bei surinko 16 naudingumo balų. Serbas ketvirtajame kėlinyje labai bangavo, keliskart suklysdamas paprastose situacijose, kaip išsimetimas iš užribio. Ką reiškia treneriui dirbti su tokiu žaidėju, kurio lygis gali kardinaliai keistis kiekvieną ataką? „Nežinau, kaip vadinate šiuos vaistus Lietuvoje, bet „Xanax“ (aut. past. itin stiprūs raminamieji vaistai). Žinote „Xanax“? – su šypsena klausė Trinchieri. – Bet aš myliu šį vyruką. Jo talentas puikiai matosi. Vėliau kai turi žaidėją, turi du pasirinkimus. Gali koncentruotis į dalykus, kuriuos jis gali padaryti, arba koncentruojiesi į jo trūkumus. Aš renkuosi koncentruotis į jo talentą. Kai kuriais momentais tikrai noriu jį pasmaugti. Bet tai vadinama komplikuota meile.“ – „Žalgiris“ laimėjo prieš „Partizan“ pirmąkart nuo 2014 metų. Ar tai skamba realistiškai?– Nesu žmogus, kuris žiūrėtų į tokius dalykus. Man visada garbė žaisti su „Partizan“. Ten yra daug draugų, kuriuos labai gerbiu. Jie turi geriausią Europos trenerį. Gaila, kad jie iškrito iš kovos dėl įkrintamųjų, bet tai buvo paskutinės mūsų namų rungtynės. Turėjome gerbti save, gerbti fanus ir gerbti varžovą. Žaidėme vadovaudamiesi šiais dalykais. – Pirmą kartą šį sezoną laimėjote rungtynes, pataikydami mažiau nei 6 tritaškius. Ką tai sako apie komandos pasirodymą?– Pasakysiu svarbiausią šių rungtynių skaičių, kuris yra 39 – atkovoti kamuoliai. Iggy (Ignas Brazdeikis) paėmė 8 atkovotus kamuolius. Jis graibstė kamuolius nuo jų atletiškų puolėjų, o ir apskritai visi prisidėjo kovoje dėl kamuolių. Buvo labai sunku žibėti puolime. Sylvainas (Francisco) nebuvo toks aštrus, kaip įprasta. Jis pataikė svarbų tritaškį, kuris pakeitė ritmą. Bet Iggy ir Sylvainas pataikė 1 iš 15 tritaškių. Dėl to galima pagirti „Partizan“ gynybą. Tačiau tai buvo kietos rungtynės, žemiau 70 taškų. Dėl to reikėjo gintis. Svarbiausia, kad žaidėme gerai gynyboje, periminėjome kamuolius, apsunkinome metimus, gerai rotavome ir atsikovojome kamuolius. Net tada, kai nepataikėme kitoje aikštės pusėje. Man tai yra puikus brandos ženklas. – Eurolygos duomenimis, tai yra jūsų pirmoji pergalė prieš Željko Obradovičių per 9 bandymus. Ar dėl to yra šiek tiek saldžiau?– Ne. Man patinka žaisti su Željko ir panašiais treneriais, nes tai yra aukščiausias lygis. Arba laimėsi, arba pasimokysi. Galiausiai žaidžia žaidėjai, o aš treniruoju. Mano žaidėjai padarė reikiamus dalykus, jog užsitikrintume pergalę. – Carlikas Jonesas pelnė 16 taškų pirmojoje pusėje...– Negalėjome jo pagauti, kadangi jis buvo tarsi peilis svieste. Mes buvome sviestas. Antrojoje pusėje visa komanda pasitempė. Arnas (Butkevičius), Bryantas (Dunstonas), net Alenas. Svarbiausia buvo, kad kai dukart jis įveikė gynybą, mes aukojome kūnus ir išprovokavome pražangas puolime. Tai buvo raktas mūsų emocijoms. Pajutome, kad galime laimėti rungtynes. – Ignas Brazdeikis sakė, kad pradėjote labiau pasitikėti juo. Kada jūs pradėjote labiau tikėti Brazdeikiu?– Tada, kai jis pradėjo labiau tikėti manimi. – Eurolygos „Top 10“ paveikslas jau beveik aiškus, tik Milano ekipa turi šansų pakilti į ten. Kas jūsų tamsusis arkliukas lenktynėse dėl titulo?– Nesakysiu komandos pavadinimo, bet tikiuosi suprasite iš mano atsakymo. Aš visada tikėjau, kad ekipa, kuri į atkrintamąsias, įkrintamąsias ar finalo ketvertą atvyksta po kančių, sunkių momentų, turi kažką daugiau. Tie, kurie iki finalo ketverto nueina tiesiu keliu, dažniausiai nepasiekia titulo. Francisco komentarai: Smailagičiaus komentarai:
title_translated: Trinchieri - about challenges with pointed and first defeated Obradovich

We played the tragic second half, concentrating only on the offensive. We did not stop Carlik Jones not once. But in the second half we played the way we should. Both teams could win, but we were well suffered at the end. The Trinchieri asked with a smile. - But I love this guy. His talent is perfectly visible. Later, when you have a player, you have two choices. You can focus on things he can do, or concentrate on its flaws. I choose to concentrate on his talent. At some moments, I really want to strangle it. But it's called complicated love. ” - Žalgiris won against Partizan for the first time since 2014. Does it sound realistic? - I'm not a man who would look at such things. I am always honored to play with Partizan. There are many friends I have a lot of respect for. They have the best European coach. It is a pity that they fell out of the fight for the Christmas Eve, but it was the last match of our home. We had to respect ourselves, respect fans and respect the opponent. We played in accordance with these things. - For the first time this season you won the match with less than 6 three -pointers. What does it say about the team's performance? - I'll tell you the most important number of the match in the match

title: Sirgaliams dėkojęs Francisco: „Kartais matau tuos pačius žmones, bet vis tiek pasirašau“
description: Kai žurnalistams buvo leista įeiti į Kauno „Žalgirio“ rūbinę, Sylvainas Francisco išsmuko ir prisistatė prie jo laukusių sirgalių, kuriems buvo pasižadėjęs. Prancūzas po laimėtų rungtynių prieš Belgrado „Partizan“ davė interviu televizijai, o baigus pasigirdo grupelės laukusių fanų šūksniai. Francisco šūktelėjo, jog pasirodys už kelių minučių, ir laikėsi savo žodžio. „Tiesiog skiriu laiko vaikams, visiems sirgaliams, – šypsojosi Francisco. – Kartais matau tuos pačius žmones, bet vis tiek pasirašau, nes jie su mumis yra nuo pradžios iki pabaigos. Man svarbiausia, kad jie ateina palaikyti mūsų, todėl noriu jiems atsilyginti savo laiku.“ „Žalgiris“ Eurolygos sezoną namuose uždarė 70:66 įveikęs Belgrado „Partizan“. Lietuvos grandas prieš šį legendinį klubą iki tol buvo patyręs šešis pralaimėjimus iš eilės. Andrea Trinchieri auklėtiniai iš 17 namų rungtynių laimėjo 10. Praėjusį sezoną kauniečiai prie savų sirgalių iškovojo 9 pergales. Visi Eurolygos namų susitikimai vyko prie sausakimšų tribūnų – buvo išparduoti visi bilietai. „Tobula, – komentavo Francisco. – Tai beprotiška, nes kai kuriose komandose, jei tikslas lieka nepasiektas, sirgaliai tiesiog nebeateina. Bet mūsų sirgaliai visada yra su mumis iki pat sezono pabaigos. Tai man labiausiai patinka.“ Francisco prametė pirmus šešis tolimus metimus, bet galiausiai ledus pralaužė lemiamu metu – įmetė septintuoju bandymu ir suteikė „Žalgiriui“ tvirtesnį pranašumą (66:62) likus žaisti pustrečios minutės. „Pradžioje pramečiau du gerus metimus iš toli, – sakė Prancūzijos rinktinės žaidėjas. – Jaučiau, kad pataikysiu, bet pramečiau. O paskutinis buvo svarbiausias. Treneris man sakė, kad mano metimo forma buvo labai bloga, jog taip negalima mesti.“ Francisco ketvirtajame kėlinyje sumetė 7 iš 21 „Žalgirio“ taško, o mačą baigė su 15 taškų (5/7 dvit., 1/9 trit., 2/2 baud.) ir 15 naudingumo balų. – Nusileidote ant Lauryno Biručio kojos ir pasisukote čiurną. Kiek tai buvo skausminga?– Buvo skausminga, bet ne taip skausminga, kaip prieš Džananą Musą. Neturėjau erdvės nusileisti po metimo. Skaudėjo, bet grįžau į rungtynes. Turiu stiprias čiurnas, tad viskas buvo gerai. – Apibendrinant jūsų sezoną – kokius didžiausius žingsnius padarėte kaip žaidėjas ir kaip žmogus?– Manau, kad vis dar turiu tą patį mentalitetą, bet taip pat mokausi žaisti su komandos draugais. Svarbiausia – kantrybė. Leisti žaidimui klostytis savaime, įtraukti komandos draugus. Esu labai konkurencingas. Kartais, kai kažkas mane erzina ar supykstu, prarandu koncentraciją. Todėl daug dirbau su tuo – skaičiau knygas, kalbėjausi su treneriu. Tai man labai padėjo. – Kokio kiekio marškinėlių reikėtų, jog galėtumėte išpildyti visų prašančių sirgalių norus?– Daug. Aš neskaičiuoju. Man tai nėra svarbu. Svarbiausia – meilė ir noras daryti tai, ką darau. Tiesiog dėkoju žmonėms, kad ateina mūsų palaikyti. – Ką komandai reikia patobulinti, kad kitą sezoną būtumėte konkurencingesni Eurolygoje?– Manau, būsime geri. Esu tikras, kad daug žaidėjų liks kitam sezonui. Turime gerą pagrindą, kad būtume dar konkurencingesni. – Ko išmokote iš Andrea Trinchieri per šį Eurolygos sezoną?– Jis labai protingas. Žino, kaip išnaudoti mano stipriąsias puses ir padėti komandos draugams. Jis nori, kad gerai ginčiausi ir klausyčiau jo nurodymų. Man labai patinka, kad su juo galiu kalbėtis, išsakyti savo nuomonę. Džiaugiuosi, kad dar vienerius metus turėsiu galimybę su juo dirbti.
title_translated: Thanks to fans Francisco: "Sometimes I see the same people, but I still sign"
description_translated: When journalists were allowed to enter the cloakroom of Kaunas Žalgiris, Sylvain Francisco dropped out and introduced himself to the fans who had pledged. After winning the match against the Belgrade Partizan, the Frenchman gave an interview to television, and after the end of the group, a group of fans awaited. Francisco shouted that he would appear in a few minutes and followed his word. "I just spend time on kids, all supporters," smiled Francisco. "Sometimes I see the same people, but I still sign because they are with us from start to finish. The most important thing for me is that they come to support us, so I want to reward them in time." Žalgiris closed the Euroleague season at home by defeating Belgrade's Partizan at 70:66. The Lithuanian Grand had suffered six consecutive defeats before this legendary club. Andrea Trinchieri students won 10 from a 17 home match. Last season, Kaunas players won 9 victories to their supporters. All Euroleague Home Meetings took place at the dry grandstands - all tickets were sold out. "It's perfect," commented Francisco. "It's crazy because some teams, if the goal remains unattended, just fans are no longer. But our fans are always with us until the end of the season. I like it most." Francisco missed the first six long -range throws, but eventually broke the ice at a crucial time - scored in the seventh attempt and gave Žalgiris a stronger advantage (66:62) to play half a minute. "In the beginning, I hit two good throws from afar," said the French team player. "I felt like I would hit, but the last one was the most important. The coach told me that my throw form was very bad that it couldn't quit." In the Francisco fourth quarter, 7 of the 21 "Grunwald" point, and finished the match with 15 points (5/7 doubles, 1/9 trit., 2/2 penalty) and 15 utility points. - You landed on the legs of Laurynas Birutis and turned the ankle. How painful it was? - It was painful but not as painful as Janan Musa. I had no space to land after a throw. It hurt but I came back to the match. I have strong ankle, so everything was fine. - Summarizing your season - what biggest steps did you make as a player and as a person? - I think I still have the same mentality, but I am also learning to play with teammates. The most important thing is patience

title_translated: Putin can no longer complete the war, even if he would like it - Foreign Policy

title_translated: A drunken policeman's motorcycle in a drunken cop in Varėna district turned

title: Lietuvių susidūrime – Sedekerskio taškų rekordas ir solidus Gebenas
description: Ispanijoje įvyko trijų lietuvių susidūrimas, kuriame rezultatyvumo rekordą fiksavo Tadas Sedekerskis. Jo atstovaujama Vitorijos „Baskonia“ (13-13) namie 92:76 (22:11, 24:24, 27:23, 19:18) įveikė Žironos „Basquet“ (9-17) su Martinu Gebenu ir Mindaugu Sušinsku. Sedekerskis per 28 minutes pelnė 24 taškus (5/5 dvit., 4/5 trit., 2/3 baud.), atkovojo 4 ir 1 kamuolį perėmė, atliko 2 rezultatyvius perdavimus, blokavo 2 metimus, kartą klydo bei įsirašė 31 naudingumo balą. Neringiškis pagerino savo asmeninį rezultatyvumo rekordą su „Baskonia“ klubo marškinėliais, kuris iki šiol siekė 23 taškus į Palensijos „Zunder“ krepšį praėjusių metų balandį. Puolėjas taip pat pakartoji įmestų tritaškių rekordą. Pralaimėjusių gretose solidžiausiai rungtyniavo Gebenas, per 20 surinkęs 15 taškų (2/2 dvit., 3/3 trit., 2/3 baud.), 5 sugriebtus ir 1 perimtą kamuolį, klaidą bei 21 efektyvumo balą. Pirmą kartą koncertai vyks Kauno istoriniame Pelėdų kalne ir Ąžuolyno bibliotekoje. Aštuoni koncertai bus nemokami. Festivalio renginiai taip pat vyks Jiezne, Prienuose, Žiežmariuose, Rietave, Birštone ir Jonavoje, rašoma organizatorių pranešime žiniasklaidai.
title_translated: Pažaislis Music Festival presents thirtieth season
description_translated: "If music knows you once ..." - this slogan will give meaning to and accompany thirty musical summer in Pažaislis. 31 May. The Pažaislis Music Festival will begin in Kaunas for three months. A variety of genres and musical styles await the thirty concert program. For the first time, concerts will be held at Kaunas Historical Owl Hill and Oak Library. Eight concerts will be free. The festival's events will also take place in Jiezne, Prienai, Žiežmariai, Rietavas, Birštonas and Jonava, according to a news release from the organizers.

title: „Moterų ralio“ užkulisiai: kokias dalyvių paslaptis organizatoriams atskleidžia technologijos?
description: „Moterų ralis“ – tai ne tik geros emocijos bei adrenalino kupinos akimirkos, puošnūs dalyvių ekipažai, netikėtos užduotys, aplankytos vaizdingos Lietuvos vietos, bet ir nemenkas iššūkis organizatoriams, teigia vienas iš „Moterų ralio“ organizatorių Maris Simson. Pasak jo, šiuolaikiniai automobilių sporto renginiai, ar tai būtų „Moterų ralis“, ar kitos varžybos, neįsivaizduojami be telematikos sprendimų, užtikrinančių sklandų dalyvių judėjimo valdymą.
title_translated: Behind the scenes of the Women's Rally: What secrets of participants do the organizers reveal to the technology?
description_translated: The Women's Rally is not only good emotions and adrenaline moments, ornate crews of participants, unexpected tasks, visited picturesque places of Lithuania, but also a great challenge for the organizers, says Maris Simson, one of the organizers of the Women's Rally. According to him, contemporary motor sports events, be it a "female rally" or other competitions, are inconceivable without telematics solutions to ensure smooth movement of participants.

title: Gyventojai dalinasi per Lietuvą keliaujančia pūga – sugrįžo tikra žiema
description: Kone visoje Lietuvoje šiąnakt ir ryte gyventojus užklupo sugrįžusi žiema. Gyventojai socialiniuose tinkluose dalinasi iškritusio sniego vaizdais, gana ekstremalios sąlygos laukia ir vairuotojų kelyje. Nuo pat ketvirtadienio ryto Lietuvoje vyrauja tikra žiema, o krentantis sniegas stebina gyventojus, kurie užklupusiais orais aktyviai dalinasi socialiniuose tinkluose.
title_translated: Residents share a storm traveling through Lithuania - a real winter returned
description_translated: Almost all over Lithuania tonight and in the morning, the residents were caught in winter. Residents on social networks share images of falling snow, and quite extreme conditions are waiting for drivers on the road. Since Thursday morning, Lithuania has a real winter, and falling snow is amazed by residents who are actively sharing the weather on social networks.

title: Siekiant uždrausti papildomas priemokas už gydymą, SAM peržiūrės ir paslaugų įkainius
description: Sveikatos apsaugos ministerijai (SAM) siūlant nuo 2026 metų visiškai uždrausti viešosioms ir privačioms gydymo įstaigoms imti papildomas priemokas už valstybės finansuojamas paslaugas, ministrė Marija Jakubauskienė žada peržiūrėti įkainius už šias paslaugas.
title_translated: In order to prohibit additional bonuses for treatment, SAM will also review service rates
description_translated: When proposing to the Ministry of Health (SAM) from 2026, the Minister Marija Jakubauskienė promises to review the rates for these services from 2026.

title: Gintautas Paluckas: pataisos dėl NT mokesčio gali būti teikiamos atskirai ir vėliau
description: Premjeras Gintautas Paluckas sako, kad itin daug diskusijų keliančios pataisos dėl naujo nekilnojamojo turto (NT) mokesčio gali būti teikiamos atskirai nuo viso mokesčių paketo ir kiek vėliau.
title_translated: Gintautas Paluckas: Amendments to real estate tax may be provided separately and later
description_translated: Prime Minister Gintautas Paluckas says that a lot of debate on the new real estate (real estate) tax can be provided separately from the total tax package and later.

title: G. Nausėda su A. Duda sutarė toliau stiprinti NATO rytinį flangą, paramą Ukrainai
description: Prezidentas Gitanas Nausėda su Lenkijos vadovu Andrzejumi Duda (Andžejumi Duda) sutarė tęsti NATO rytinio flango stiprinimą ir paramos teikimą Ukrainai iki jos visapusės pergalės prieš Rusiją.
title_translated: G. Nausėda and A. Duda agreed to further strengthen NATO's eastern flank, support for Ukraine
description_translated: President Gitanas Nausėda agreed with Polish leader Andrzej Duda (Andrew Duda), to continue NATO's eastern flang and support for Ukraine to its full victory over Russia.

title: Iš esmės keis ligos išmokų tvarką: pats žmogus spręs, kada turi gauti pinigų susirgęs?
description: Šiuo metu pripažinti žmogų laikinai nedarbingu gali tik gydytojai. Jų sprendimas yra pagrindas darbuotojui mokėti ligos išmoką. Tačiau Sveikatos apsaugos ministerija siūlo, kad pats žmogus spręstų, ar tikrai serga, o kartu ir ar už tai jam priklauso pinigai.
title_translated: The procedure for illness benefits will change essentially: the person will decide when to get the money when he is ill?
description_translated: Currently, only doctors can recognize a person temporarily incapacitated. Their solution is the basis for the employee to pay the sickness benefit. However, the Ministry of Health proposes that the person himself decides whether he is really sick, and whether he owns money.

title: JAV lietuvis: Trumpo politika skaldo JAV, bet dalis lietuvių palaiko šalies persitvarkymą
description: JAV prezidentas Donaldas Trumpas, ateidamas į postą, žadėjo būti Amerikos vienytoju, tačiau įvairiuose Amerikos miestuose vilnijo protestai prieš prezidento vykdomą politiką. JAV gyvenantis lietuvis Laurynas Misevičius sako, kad vienijimas kol kas stringa, o protestai gali peraugti į smurtinius susirėmimus.
title_translated: US Lithuanian: Trump's policy breaks in the US but some Lithuanian supports the country's reorganization
description_translated: US President Donald Trump, coming to the post, promised to be an American unity, but in various American cities, protests against the president's policy in various American cities. Laurynas Misevičius, a Lithuanian living in the US, says that unification is still getting stuck, and protests can grow into violent clashes.

title: Skandalas oro uoste: pusnuogė moteris šokiravo keleivius – visi liko be žado
description: Praėjusią savaitę Fort Loderdeilio-Holivudo (JAV) tarptautiniame oro uoste viduryje ginčo iki pusės nusirengė viena keleivė. Toks šios moters poelgis prisidėjo prie vis didėjančios tendencijos nusirengti skrydžio metu ar oro uoste.
title_translated: Scandal at the airport: a half -naked woman shocked passengers - all left without a promise
description_translated: Last week, Fort Loderdio-Hollywood (USA) at the middle of the international airport was undressed by one passenger. This woman's attitude contributed to the increasing tendency to undress in flight or at the airport.

title: Sunku patikėti: Austrijos startuolis gamina alų iš šlapimo
description: Austrijos bendrovė „öKlo“, bendradarbiaudama su Vienos žemės ūkio ir aplinkosaugos mokslų universitetu (BOKU) ir vietos alaus darykla, pradėjo projektą, pagal kurį alus bus gaminamas naudojant žmogaus šlapimą kaip vieną iš žaliavų.
title_translated: Hard to believe: Austrian startup produces beer from urine
description_translated: The Austrian company Öklo, in cooperation with the University of Agricultural and Environmental Sciences (Boku) and the local brewery, launched a project to produce beer with human urine as one of the raw materials.

title: Turkijoje sulaikyti du tyrimų žurnalistai
description: Turkijoje atliekant tyrimą dėl vienos televizijos pardavimo ketvirtadienį buvo sulaikyti du tyrimų žurnalistai, pranešė Stambulo prokuratūra.
title_translated: Two research journalists were detained in Turkey
description_translated: Two investigation reporters were detained on Thursday in Turkey to sell one television, the Istanbul Prosecutor's Office said.

title: „Trailo Kalvės“ sezono finišas – dalyviai rinks pakilimus Alytuje
description: Bekelės bėgimo varžybos „Trailo Kalvė“ artėjantį sekmadienį (balandžio 13 d.) kviečia į šeštąjį ir paskutinį 2024–2025 m. sezono etapą, kuris taps ir sezono finalu. Šįkart varžybos vyks Alytuje, kur bekelės bėgimo mėgėjai suras tikrai nemažai vertikalių metrų, rašoma pranešime žiniasklaidai.
title_translated: The Treilo Blacksmiths' finish - participants will pick ups in Alytus
description_translated: The off -road running competition "Trail Kalvė" invites to the sixth and last 2024-2025 on the upcoming Sunday (April 13). The season stage, which will also become the season of the season. This time the competition will take place in Alytus, where off -road running lovers will find quite a few vertical meters, according to a news release.

title: Rinktinė, kokios nėra buvę: „Savo tikslo siekiame tyliai“
description: Jungtinės Amerikos Valstijos, Kanada, Švedija, Suomija, Šveicarija – tai šalys, kuriose ledo ritulio paslapčių mokosi talentingiausias mūsų jaunimas. Jau šį savaitgalį Kauno ledo rūmuose jis bandys žengti istorinį žingsnį – į pasaulio U18 čempionato I-ojo diviziono A grupę.
title_translated: A team that has never happened: "We are pursuing the goal quietly"
description_translated: The United States, Canada, Sweden, Finland, Switzerland are countries where our most talented young people learn the secrets of hockey. Already this weekend, he will try to take a historical step at the Kaunas Ice Palace-Group A of the World U18 Championship Division I.

title: Atamanas nebesitiki sulaukti Grigonio: „Nematau, kaip tai galėtų įvykti“
description: Erginas Atamanas spaudos konferencijoje prieš Atėnų „Panathinaikos“ ir Belgrado „Crvena Zvezda“ rungtynes aptarė įvairias temas, įskaitant ir Mariaus Grigonio situaciją. Treneris dar vasario pradžioje kalbėjo, jog laukia lietuvio sugrįžimo į aikštę už kelių savaičių, tačiau šiuo metu džiuginančių žinių neturėjo bei pareiškė, jog nesitiki išvysti Grigonio ir atkrintamosiose rungtynėse. „Nemanau, kad (Grigonis) galės žaisti atkrintamosiose, – kalbėjo turkas. – Jis jau beveik šešis mėnesius nedalyvavo komandos treniruotėse, tad nematau, kaip tai galėtų įvykti.“ Kaunietis nerungtyniauja nuo spalio mėnesio bei sveiksta po nugaros operacijos, kurios prireikė nepasiteisinus konservatyviam gydymui. Po traumos atsigaunantis Grigonis – apie sprendimą dėl rinktinės ir svarbiausią žaidėją „Žalgiryje” Smunkantis Lietuvos krepšinio įvaizdis ir kodėl Jokubaitis neskuba į „Žalgirį“? | BN+ Q&A:
title_translated: Ataman no longer expects Grigonis: "I don't see how it could happen"
description_translated: Ergin Ataman discussed a variety of topics at the Panathinaikos and Belgrade Crvena Zvezda at the press conference against Athens' Panathinaikos and Belgrade. The coach said in early February that he was waiting for a Lithuanian return to the square a few weeks, but he had no joy at the moment and stated that he was not expecting to see Grigonis and playoffs. "I don't think (Grigonis) will be able to play in the playoffs," Turkish said. "He hasn't participated in team training for almost six months, so I don't see how it could happen." Kaunas does not play since October and heal after a back surgery, which was needed without a conservative treatment. Grigonis, who is recovering after the injury, is about the decision of the national team and the most important player in Žalgiris, the image of Lithuanian basketball and why Jokubaitis is in no hurry to Žalgiris? | Bn q

title: Stebuklingas dyzelinis „Volkswagen“: 100 km – tik 1,7 l degalų
description: Esame pratę prie to, kad technologijos šuoliais juda į priekį. Šiuolaikinių automobilių vidaus degimo varikliai yra labai ekonomiški, o seni – nešvarūs ir labai alkani. O gal ne?
title_translated: Magical Diesel Volkswagen: 100 km - only 1.7 l fuel
description_translated: We are used to the fact that technology jumps forward. Modern car internal combustion engines are very economical and old are dirty and very hungry. Or maybe not?

title: Eimantas Stanionis: apie kitokį Enniso stilių, kovą primenančius sparingus, „ausinių“ gynybą, neaktyvumą ir buvusias mintis apie pasitraukimą iš bokso
description: Jau balandžio 13-osios ankstyvą rytą Lietuvos laiku „Boardwalk Hall“ arenoje Atlantik Sičio mieste Naujojo Džersio valstijoje Eimantas Stanionis (15-0, 1 be nugalėtojo, 9 nokautai) gins WBA pusvidutinio svorio kategorijos čempiono diržą, kai stos į svarbiausią karjeros kovą prieš IBF čempioną Jaronas „Bootsą“ Ennisą (33-0, 1 be nugalėtojo, 29 nokautai). Šioje kovoje taip pat bus kovojama ir dėl laisvojo „The Ring“ čempiono diržo.
title_translated: Eimantas Stanionis: About a different style of Ennisis, a struggle -like sparring, "headphones" defense, inactivity and former thoughts about withdrawal from boxing
description_translated: Already in the early morning of April 13, Eimantas Stanionis (15-0, 1 without winner, 9 knockout) will defend the WBA Consumer Weight Champion Belt at the Boardwalk Hall City of New Jersey, at the Atlantic City of New Jersey. winner, 29 knockout). This struggle will also fight for the free Strap of The Ring champion.

title: Fiksuoti dantų protezai: modernus sprendimas, keičiantis gyvenimus
description: Dantų netekimas – ne tik estetinė, bet ir funkcinė bei psichologinė problema, su kuria susiduria daugybė žmonių. Nors šiandien odontologija siūlo daugybę modernių sprendimų, daugelis pacientų vis dar nežino, kad galima atkurti visus dantis vos per kelias dienas – estetiškai, patikimai ir be ilgo laukimo. Apie dantų atkūrimo fiksuotais dantų protezais galimybes pasakoja odontologijos klinikos „Precize“ gydytoja odontologe Gintarė Žmuidinavičienė.
title_translated: Fixed dentures: a modern solution that changes lives
description_translated: Teeth loss is not only aesthetic but also a functional and psychological problem that many people face. Although dentistry today offers many modern solutions, many patients still do not know that all their teeth can be restored in just a few days - aesthetically, reliably and without long wait. Gintarė Žmuidinavičienė, a dentist of the dental clinic, tells about the possibilities of dental restoration with fixed dental prostheses.

title: Asteroidui suteiktas VU profesoriaus, Baroko epochos poeto vardas
description: Vilniaus universiteto (VU) profesoriaus, Baroko epochos poeto Motiejaus Kazimiero Sarbievijaus (1595–1640) vardu pavadintas asteroidas „Sarbievius“. Asteroidą atrado VU Fizikos fakulteto Teorinės fizikos ir astronomijos instituto mokslininkas dr. Kazimieras Černis VU Molėtų astronomijos observatorijoje, rašoma VU pranešime žiniasklaidai.
title_translated: The name of the asteroid was awarded the name of the VU professor, the Baroque Era poet
description_translated: The asteroid "Sarbievius" was named after Motiejus Sarbievijus (1595-1640), a professor of Vilnius University (VU), a Baroque poet of Vilnius University (VU). The asteroid was discovered by dr. Kazimieras Chernis at VU Molėtai Astronomical Observatory, according to a news release from VU.

title: Šie įdaryti kiaušiniai puikiai tiks Velykų stalui: receptą užsirašykite jau dabar
description: „Šventinio Velykų stalo patiekalas – gardūs įdaryti kiaušiniai. Šis receptas tiks ir po Velykų, kai lieka kiaušinių, o valgyti įprastai jų jau nebesinori“, – sako tinklaraštininkė Rasa. Reikės: Kiaušinių (kietai virtų) – 8 vnt.; Rūkytos šoninės plonai pjaustytų juostelių (pakepintų) – 4–5vnt.; Marinuotų mažų agurkėlių – 2 vnt.; Majonezo – 1/4 puodelio(1 puodelis 240 ml); geltonųjų garstyčių – 1/2 arb.šaukštelio; Marinuotų agurkėlių skysčio – 2 arb.
title_translated: These stuffed eggs will be perfect for the Easter table: write down the recipe now
description_translated: "The festive Easter table dish is delicious stuffed eggs. This recipe will be suitable after Easter, when they remain eggs, and you don't want to eat them usually," says blogger Rasa. You will need: eggs (hard cooked) - 8 pieces; Smoked bacon thinly sliced ​​strips (fried) - 4-5pcs; Marinated small cucumbers - 2 pieces; Mayonnaise - 1/4 cup (1 cup 240 ml); yellow mustard - 1/2 tbsp; Marinated cucumber fluid - 2 tbsp.

title: Norvegija siekia lytinius santykius be sutikimo pripažinti išžaginimu
description: Norvegijos parlamentui ketvirtadienį buvo pateiktas įstatymo projektas, pagal kurį lytiniai santykiai be sutikimo būtų laikomi išžaginimu.
title_translated: Norway seeks sexual intercourse without consent to recognize rape
description_translated: A bill was submitted to the Norwegian parliament on Thursday, according to which sexual intercourse would be considered as rape.

title: E. pinigų ir mokėjimo įstaigoms suteikta prieiga prie europinių mokėjimo sistemų
description: Mokėjimo paslaugas teikiančioms elektroninių pinigų (EPĮ) ir mokėjimo įstaigoms (MĮ) suteikta prieiga prie mokėjimo sistemų visoje Europoje, įskaitant ir centrinių bankų valdomas mažmeninių mokėjimų sistemas.
title_translated: E. Money and Payment Institutions have been given access to European payment systems
description_translated: Payment services for electronic money (EPC) and payment institutions (MS) have been provided with payment systems throughout Europe, including central banks controlled by retail payment systems.

title: Klaipėdiečiai kviečiami suteikti nereikalingiems dviračiams antrą gyvenimą
description: Klaipėdoje startuoja iniciatyva, kuri sujungia socialinę atsakomybę, aplinkosaugą ir bendruomeniškumą. Organizacija „Draugas Draugui“ kviečia visus geros valios žmones prisidėti prie akcijos – paaukoti nereikalingus dviračius, paspirtukus, riedlentes ar riedučius, kad jie įgytų antrą gyvenimą. Surinktos ir suremontuotos transporto priemonės bus padovanotos remtinoms šeimoms, Raudonajam Kryžiui, Caritas organizacijoms, o nuo likusių parduoti dviračių surinktas pelnas bus skirtas VšĮ „Gyvenam“ bei Lietuvos Dauno sindromo asociacijai, skelbiama organizacijos „Draugas Draugui“ pranešime žiniasklaidai.
title_translated: Klaipeda residents are invited to give unnecessary bikes a second life
description_translated: In Klaipeda, an initiative starts, which combines social responsibility, environmental protection and community. The Friend organization invites all people of good will to contribute to the campaign - donating unnecessary bikes, scooters, skateboarding or roller skates to gain a second life. The vehicles collected and renovated will be donated to disadvantaged families, the Red Cross, Tsaritas organizations, and the bicycle -collected profits will be dedicated to the public institution "Living" and the Lithuanian Association of Down Syndrome, according to a news release from a friend.

title: Krova Rygos uoste pirmąjį metų ketvirtį sumenko 7,6 proc.
description: Rygos uostas – didžiausias pagal krovos apimtis Latvijos uostas – pranešė per pirmąjį šių metų ketvirtį perkrovęs 4,352 mln. tonų krovinių – 7,6 proc. mažiau nei per tą patį laikotarpį pernai.
title_translated: Carriage in Riga port in the first quarter of the year decreased by 7.6 percent.
description_translated: The port of Riga - the largest Latvian port of Latvia - announced in the first quarter of this year, which rebuilt $ 4.352 million. tons of cargo - 7.6 percent. less than during the same period last year.

title: E.pinigų ir mokėjimo įstaigoms suteikta prieiga prie europinių mokėjimo sistemų
description: Mokėjimo paslaugas teikiančioms elektroninių pinigų (EPĮ) ir mokėjimo įstaigoms (MĮ) suteikta prieiga prie mokėjimo sistemų visoje Europoje, įskaitant ir centrinių bankų valdomas mažmeninių mokėjimų sistemas.
title_translated: E.Pinigins and payment institutions have been given access to European payment systems
description_translated: Payment services for electronic money (EPC) and payment institutions (MS) have been provided with payment systems throughout Europe, including central banks controlled by retail payment systems.

title: Rusų žvalgybos pareigūnas: Rusija su JAV aptars daugiau apsikeitimų kaliniais
description: Maskvos užsienio žvalgybos tarnybos vadovas penktadienį pranešė, kad Rusija su Jungtinėmis Valstijomis aptars daugiau apsikeitimų kaliniais po šią savaitę įvykusių mainų.
title_translated: Russian intelligence officer: Russia will discuss more swaps in prisoners
description_translated: The head of the Moscow Foreign Intelligence Service said Friday that Russia would discuss more exchanges with the United States with prisoners after the exchange this week.

title: Pirmieji nesutarimai „Ferrari“ F1 komandoje: žodį tarė Charlesas Leclercas
description: Pranešama, kad Charlesas Leclercas išreiškė nusivylimą „Ferrari“ komandoje susidariusia situacija, kai, jo nuomone, Lewiso Hamiltono pusė pradeda dominuoti priimant sprendimus.
title_translated: The first disagreements in the Ferrari F1 team: the word was said by Charles Leclercas
description_translated: Charles Leclerc is reportedly expressing frustration with the situation in the Ferrari team, when he believes Lewis Hamilton begins to dominate the decision.

title: Skvernelis: turime rodyti pavyzdį taupydami, bet „vienas kurpalis“ visiems netinka
description: Seimo pirmininkas Saulius Skvernelis sako, kad viešasis sektorius turi rodyti pavyzdį taupydamas lėšas, tačiau pabrėžia, kad negalima visų institucijų vertinti „pagal vieną kurpalį“. Taip jis kalbėjo Finansų ministerijai siūlant Vyriausybei įpareigoti kiekvieną ministeriją, išskyrus Krašto apsaugos, nuo kitų metų po 5 proc. mažinti išlaidas. „Tikrai sutinku, kad viešajam sektoriui reikia rodyti pavyzdį ir ten, kur išlaidos yra nebūtinos, jas reikia karpyti.
title_translated: Skvernel: We have to set an example of saving but "one shoe" is not suitable for everyone
description_translated: Speaker of the Seimas Saulius Skvernelis says that the public sector must set an example for saving funds, but emphasizes that all institutions cannot be evaluated by "one shoe". In this way, he spoke to the Ministry of Finance proposed to the Government to oblige every ministry, except for national defense, from next year after 5 %. to reduce costs. “I really agree that the public sector needs an example and where the costs are unnecessary, they need to be cut.

title: „Tikiuosi, kad teisėjai dirbs sąžiningai“: Stanionio treneris papasakojo, kaip ruošė lietuvį kovai su Ennisu
description: Jau ankstyvą šio sekmadienio rytą Lietuvos laiku Eimantas Stanionis (15-0, 1 be nugalėtojo, 9 nokautai) ir Jaronas „Bootsas“ Ennisas (33-0, 1 be nugalėtojo, 29 nokautai) „Boardwalk Hall“ arenoje Atlantik Sičio mieste Naujojo Džersio valstijoje susikaus dėl trijų pusvidutinio svorio (iki 147 svarų) kategorijos čempiono diržų: J. Ennisas gins IBF čempiono titulą, E. Stanionio vardu bus pastatytas WBA diržas, o kartu jie kovos ir dėl laisvojo „The Ring“ čempiono diržo.
title_translated: "I hope the judges will work honestly": Stanionis coach told how he was preparing a Lithuanian to fight Ennisu
description_translated: Already early this Sunday morning Lithuanian time Eimantas Stanionis (15-0, 1 without winner, 9 knockout) and Jaron Boots ennis (33-0, 1 without winner, 29 Nokauts) in the Boardwalk Hall Arena in Atlantic City of New Jersey in the New Jersey State Ennis will defend the title of IBF champion, the WBA belt will be built on behalf of E. Stanionis, while they will fight for the free The Ring championship belt.

title: Seimo vadovas ragina R. Puchovičių įsivertinti galimybes tęsti darbą BFK
description: Seimo pirmininkas Saulius Skvernelis ragina tiek „Nemuno aušrą“, tiek patį partijos atstovą Seime Robertą Puchovičių įsivertinti galimybes tęsti darbą Seimo Biudžeto ir finansų komitete (BFK).
title_translated: The head of the Seimas calls Mr Puchovich to evaluate the possibilities to continue working in BFK
description_translated: Speaker of the Seimas Saulius Skvernelis urges both the Nemunas Dawn and the party's representative in the Seimas Robert Puchovich to evaluate the opportunities to continue working in the Seimas Committee on Budget and Finance (BFK).

title: JT laikinai valdė ištisas valstybes: kodėl Putino pasiūlymas dėl Ukrainos yra niekinis?
description: Rusijos autokratinis lyderis Vladimiras Putinas pasiūlė Ukrainoje įvesti laikiną Jungtinių Tautų (JT) valdymą. Portalas „Meduza“ paaiškino, kodėl tai neįmanoma, nors anksčiau ši organizacija iš tiesų kontroliavo ištisas valstybes.

title: JAV teigia, kad derybos su Iranu bus tiesioginės

title_translated: The US says negotiations with Iran will be direct
description_translated: The United States' negotiations with Iran will be direct, the White House said Friday, though Tehran denies it, both countries are preparing for a diplomatic meeting this weekend. "It will be direct negotiations with the Iranians, and I want to emphasize it very clearly," Caroline Leavitt, secretary of the White House, told reporters. "The president believes in diplomacy, direct negotiations, direct conversations in the same room," she added.

title: „Juventus“ gerina pozicijas Italijos čempionate

title: „Žalgiris“ įteikė ilgalaikę sutartį Wongui
description: Vėlų šeštadienio vakarą iš Jungtinių Amerikos Valstijų (JAV) atkeliavo netikėta žinia. „HoopsHype“ NBA apžvalgininkas Michaelas Scotto skelbia, jog Kauno „Žalgiris“ su Isaiah Wongu sukirto rankomis dėl trejų metų sutarties. Pasak Scotto, kontrakte yra galimybė šią vasarą žaidėjui išvykti į NBA, Kiniją ar kitą Eurolygos klubą. Jei ja pasinaudota nebus, Wongas Kaune liktų iki 2027-2028 m. sezono pabaigos. Wongas „Žalgirį“ papildė vasario pabaigoje bei Eurolygoje spėjo sužaisti septynerias rungtynes. title_translated: Žalgiris handed a long -term contract to Wong to
description_translated: Late Saturday night from the United States (USA) came an unexpected message. Michael Scotto, a NBA commentator at Hoopshype, announces that Kaunas Žalgiris with Isaiah Wongs has shifted his hands on a three -year contract. According to Scott, the contract is possible this summer to leave for the NBA, China or other Euroleague club. If it was not used, Wong in Kaunas would remain until 2027-2028. the end of the season. Wong added to Žalgiris at the end of February and played seven matches in the Euroleague. description_translated: Our aging is partly dependent on factors that we do not affect, such as the effects of genes or contaminants. However, research shows that aging can be influenced by our behavior, especially through sleep, physical activity and eating habits. title: „Turime penkias minutes“: ukrainiečiai parodė, kaip vykdė kraują stingdančią evakuaciją mirties keliu
description: Keturi plastikiniai maišai su asmeniniais daiktais ir vyras, gulintis ant žemės kieme. Toks buvo 74 metų Emilijos Bezrodnajos, nuo vaikystės dirbusios ūkio darbus, gyvenimas, kai ji buvo priversta bėgti iš subombarduotų namų Chersono srityje. Leidinio „Postimees“ žurnalistė dalyvavo specialioje evakuacijos operacijoje, kurios metu evakavo senolę ir jos anūką iš namų, kurie buvo ką tik sugriauti po Kremliaus atakos. Pateikiame kraują stingdantį pasakojimą – kaip atrodo evakuacija, kai mirtinas smūgis gali būti suduotas bet kurią akimirką.
title_translated: "We have five minutes": Ukrainians have shown how they performed blood -stiffening evacuation by death
description_translated: Four plastic bags with personal belongings and a man lying on the ground in the yard. Such was the life of Emilia Bezrodnaya, a 74 -year -old life of farm work since her childhood, when she was forced to flee the bombed home in the Kherson area. The Postimees journalist participated in a special evacuation operation, where she evacuated her grandmother and her grandson from home, who had just been destroyed after the Kremlin attack. We present a blood stiffening narrative - what evacuation looks like when a fatal blow can be made at any moment.

title: RKL auksas ir bilietas į „7bet-NKL“ – Kėdainių komandai
description: Regionų krepšinio lygos (RKL) A diviziono sezonas sekmadienį finišavo Kėdainiuose, kur finalinę dieną paaiškėjo tiek čempionai, tiek bronzos medalių savininkai. Vienose rungtynėse – pratęsimo drama dėl trečiosios vietos, kitose – užtikrintas lyderių dominavimas kovoje dėl titulo. Užtikrintas šeimininkų triumfas finale Kovoje dėl aukso ir vietos Nacionalinėje krepšinio lygoje („7bet-NKL“) Kėdainių sporto centro ekipa pademonstravo, kodėl buvo laikomi viso sezono favoritais – rezultatu 90:69 (29:19, 19:15, 19:19, 23:16) buvo nugalėta „Tauragė“, o pergalė iškovota be realios intrigos nuo pirmųjų minučių. Kėdainiškių triumfo pagrindas – Roko Ūzo, Lauryno Danieliaus ir Lauryno Bimbos trijulė, kuri kartu pelnė net 63 taškus. Finalo ketverto MVP tapęs Rokas Ūzas įmetė 21, Laurynas Danielius pridėjo 22, o Laurynas Bimba – 20 taškų. Be to, jie kartu atkovojo 24 kamuolius, atliko 17 rezultatyvių perdavimų ir pataikė net 20 dvitaškių iš 25. Pralaimėjusių gretose rezultatyviausias buvo Martynas Linkevičius su 16 taškų, Gvidas Galinauskas pridėjo 14. Pratęsimo drama kovoje dėl bronzos Mažajame finale „Raseiniai“ ir Vytauto Didžiojo universitetas (VDU) padovanojo žiūrovams tikrą krepšinio trilerį. Po įtemptos, aukšto tempo ir rezultatyvios kovos, bronzos medaliai atiteko Raseinių komandai – 106:102 (23:23, 26:21, 22:26, 22:23, 13:9). Kaip praėjusią savaitę pranešė „Lietuvos geležinkelių“ (LTG) grupė, savaitei nutraukiami keleivinių traukinių maršrutai Vilnius-Klaipėda-Vilnius, Klaipėda–Šiauliai–Klaipėda ir Radviliškis–Šiauliai–Klaipėda.

Šventės kulminacija tapo įspūdingas paradas atvirame autobuse, kuris riedėjo miesto gatvėmis, o komandos nariai iš jo džiaugsmingai mojavo fanams. Kaip visada dėmesio centre buvo ryškiausia asmenybė – Šarūnas Jasikevičius.
title_translated: Showed how Šarūnas Jasikevičius celebrated its historic victory: joy poured over the edges
description_translated: The winners of the Euroleague returned to Turkey with the biggest bang. On Tuesday night, Istanbulo streets filled with thousands of supporters who gathered to congratulate the new European champions. The celebration culminated in an impressive parade on an open bus that rolled down the city streets, and the team members woke up to fans. As always, the most prominent personality was Šarūnas Jasikevičius.

title: Vandens sportas be traumų: ką būtina žinoti prieš lipant ant irklentės ar į baidarę
description: Vasara – vandens sporto sezonas. Vis daugiau žmonių leidžiasi į žygius baidarėmis, atranda irklentes, banglentes, kaituoja ar tiesiog mėgaujasi aktyviu laisvalaikiu prie vandens. Šios veiklos neabejotinai stiprina kūną ir gerina savijautą, tačiau kineziterapeutai įspėja: neįvertinus krūvio ar savo galimybių, smagūs nuotykiai gali baigtis trauma, rašoma „Eglės sanatorijos“ pranešime žiniasklaidai.
title_translated: Water sports without injuries: What do you need to know before climbing on a paddle or canoe
description_translated: Summer is a water sports season. More and more people are going to kayaking, finding paddles, surfing, boiling or just enjoying active leisure to the water. These activities undoubtedly strengthen the body and improve their well -being, but physiotherapists warn that without evaluating the load or their capabilities, fun adventures can result in trauma, according to a news release from the Eglė Sanatorium.

title: Skvernelis ragina griežčiau reaguoti į incidentus Baltijos jūroje: iš esmės Estija buvo palikta viena
description: Seimo pirmininkas Saulius Skvernelis ragina Vakarus griežčiau reaguoti į pasikartojančius incidentus Baltijos jūroje. Politikas atkreipia dėmesį, kad vienam iš Rusijos šešėlinio laivyno laivų neseniai sukėlus rimtą incidentą Estijoje, ši šalis, pasak jo, sąjungininkų buvo iš esmės palikta viena. „Žiūriu su nerimu vien dėl nedrąsos ir netinkamų reakcijų į tai, kas ir Baltijos jūroje vyksta.
title_translated: Skvernel calls for a stronger response to incidents in the Baltic Sea: basically Estonia was left alone
description_translated: Speaker of the Seimas Saulius Skvernelis urges the West to respond more strictly to recurrent incidents in the Baltic Sea. The politician points out that one of Russia's shadow vessels has recently caused a serious incident in Estonia, which, according to him, was essentially left alone. “I look at anxiety just because of the timid and inappropriate reactions to what is happening in the Baltic Sea.

title: Gegužę – išankstinė 3 proc. metinė infliacija, 0,3 proc. mėnesio defliacija
description: Išankstinė metinė infliacija Lietuvoje gegužę, palyginti su tuo pačiu metu pernai, siekia 3 proc., trečiadienį skelbia Valstybės duomenų agentūra.
title_translated: In May - pre -3 percent. annual inflation, 0.3 percent. Monthly deflation
description_translated: Pre -annual inflation in Lithuania in May, compared to the same time last year, reaches 3 %, state data agency reports on Wednesday.

title: Prie Maskvos – galingas drono smūgis technologijų parkui
description: Trečiadienį dronai vėl atakavo Rusijos teritoriją, rašo UNIAN. Skelbiama, kad buvo suduotas smūgis dronų gamybos įmonei, taip pat technologijų parkui prie Maskvos. Pranešimai apie smūgius pasirodė rusų „Telegram“ kanaluose.
title_translated: Near Moscow - a powerful drone blow to the Technology Park
description_translated: On Wednesday, drones again attacked Russian territory, writes Unian. It is announced that the drone manufacturing company, as well as the technology park near Moscow, was announced. The impact reports appeared in the Russian Telegram channels.

title: Saulius Skvernelis: dėl NT mokesčio turės būti daromi kompromisai
description: Vyriausybės iš antro karto parlamentui pateiktas nekilnojamojo turto (NT) mokestis turės būti koreguojamas, kad sulauktų didesnės dalies parlamentarų palaikymo ir būtų priimtas, mano Seimo pirmininkas Saulius Skvernelis. „Pateikimas reikalingas buvo to, kad tos diskusijos persikeltų į Seimą, kas intensyviai dabar ir vyksta, registruojami pasiūlymai įvairūs. Ir reikės čia tikrai tą balansą surasti.
title_translated: Saulius Skvernelis: Due to real estate tax will have to be compromised
description_translated: The real estate (real estate) fee submitted to the parliament from the second time will have to be adjusted to receive a majority of parliamentarians and to be adopted, with the Speaker of the Seimas Saulius Skvernelis. “The submission needed was that those discussions would move to the Seimas, which is intensively now, and the proposals are registered. And you will need to find that balance here.

title: Paluckas apie savo polinkį „nesureikšminti“: „Aš turiu daugiausia informacijos, kas yra reikšminga, o kas – ne“
description: Tam tikrų klausimų „nesureikšminti“ linkęs premjeras Gintautas Paluckas teigia, kad tokį požiūrį lemia jo disponuojama informacija. Pasak jo, tai leidžia atsirinkti svarbius dalykus ir atskirti įvairius pasisakymus į skirtingas kategorijas. „Aš turiu daugiausia informacijos, kas yra reikšminga, o kas – ne. Kartais antraštėse dalykai atrodo gerokai išpūsti, negu jie yra realybėje.
title_translated: Paluck about his inclination to "not emphasize": "I have the most information that is significant and what is not" "
description_translated: Prime Minister Gintautas Paluckas, who is prone to "not to emphasize", says that this attitude is determined by the information he has. According to him, it allows you to select important things and distinguish different statements in different categories. "I have the most information about what is significant and what is not. Sometimes in the headlines things seem to be much inflated than they are in reality.

title: Pentagono vadovas susitikime su lenkų ministru Lenkiją pavadino pavyzdine sąjungininke
description: Jungtinių Valstijų gynybos sekretorius Pete'as Hegsethas (Pitas Hegsetas) antradienį susitikęs su lenkų gynybos ministru Wladyslawu Kosiniaku-Kamyszu (Vladislavu Kosiniaku-Kamišu) pareiškė, kad Lenkija ir JAV yra vieningos siekiant taikos per jėgą.
title_translated: The Pentagon leader called the Polish minister Poland as a model ally
description_translated: The United States Defense Secretary Pete Hegseth (Pitt Hegset) met with Polish Defense Minister Wladyslaw Kosiniak-Kamysz (Vladislav Kosiniaku-Kamishu) on Tuesday that Poland and the United States were united for peace.

title: „Investuok Lietuvoje“ vadovas apie TUI: gerai, kad žinome, kas vyksta, blogai, kad nieko gero
description: Elijus Čivilis, „Investuok Lietuvoje“ vadovas, teigia, kad šiuo metu visas regionas patiria daug sunkumų, o kiekviena šalis bando gerinti gebėjimus pritraukti tiesiogines užsienio investicijas (TUI). VŽ podkaste jis kalba apie investicijų greitkelio svarbą, laisvųjų ekonominių zonų plėtrą ir būdus išsiskirti tarp vidutiniokų.
title_translated: Invest in Lithuania's manager about Tui: Okay we know what's going on, bad that nothing good
description_translated: Elijus Čivilis, the head of Invest in Lithuania, says that the whole region is currently undergoing a lot of difficulties and each country is trying to improve the ability to attract direct foreign investment (FDI). He talks about the importance of the investment motorway, the development of free economic zones and ways to stand out among the average.

title: Vietoj sandėlių – dar vienas naujas kvartalas, bet kaimynai susirūpinę: „Planuoja iškirsti daug medžių“
description: Dar viena senų sandėlių teritorija Vilniuje netrukus virs gyvenamųjų namų kvartalu. Vis dėlto, atrodytų, geri pokyčiai patinka ne visiems. Dėl naujojo projekto, kuris dar tik pristatomas visuomenei, jau pasigirdo nepasitenkinimo balsų – nors namai dygs vietoj senų pastatų, piktinamasi, kad prireiks kirsti medžius. Statytojai sako, kad jiems rūpi žalias Vilnius, todėl sprendimai būsią draugiški aplinkai.
title_translated: Instead of warehouses, another new quarter, but neighbors are concerned: "Plans to cut many trees"
description_translated: Another area of ​​old warehouses in Vilnius will soon become a block of residential houses. Still, it seems like good changes are not enjoyed by everyone. The new project, which is still presented to the public, has already heard the voices of dissatisfaction - although the houses will stitch up instead of old buildings, it is angry that the trees will need to be cut. The builders say they care about green Vilnius, so the solutions will be environmentally friendly.

title: „MG grupės“ savininko Dariaus Mockaus sklypas Vilniuje užima 56 kv. metrus valstybinės žemės
description: Valstybinei teritorijų planavimo ir statybos inspekcijai (VTPSI) atlikus neplaninį patikrinimą, nustatyta, kad vienos didžiausių Lietuvoje gamybos, prekybos, nekilnojamojo turto ir žiniasklaidos grupių „MG grupės“ savininko Dariaus Mockaus ir jo sutuoktinės sklypas Vilniaus Filaretų gatvėje užima 56 kv. metrų valstybinės žemės, ketvirtadienį skelbia naujienų portalas „Delfi“.
title_translated: The plot of Darius Mockus, the owner of MG Group, occupies 56 sq. M. meters of state land
description_translated: The State Territorial Planning and Construction Inspectorate (VTPSI) conducted an unscheduled inspection, it was found that one of the largest production, trade, real estate and media groups MG Group owner Darius Mockus and his spouse on Vilniaus Filarets Street occupies 56 sq. M. meters of state land, Delfi news portal is reported on Thursday.

title: Pasienyje su Baltarusija apgręžti 20 migrantų
description: Lietuvos pasienyje su Baltarusija praėjusią parą apgręžta 20 neteisėtų migrantų, ketvirtadienį pranešė Valstybės sienos apsaugos tarnyba.
title_translated: At the border with Belarus turns 20 migrants
description_translated: 20 illegal migrants were turned on the Lithuanian border with Belarus last day, the State Border Guard Service said Thursday.

title: „Pietinia kronikas“: kultinis romanas virto stalo žaidimu
description: Didžiausia lietuviškų stalo žaidimų leidėja „Terra Publica“ išleido stalo žaidimą „Pietinia kronikas“, sukurtą pagal kultinį rašytojo Rimanto Kmitos to paties pavadinimo romaną.
title_translated: "Southern chronicles": a cult novel turned into a board game
description_translated: Terra Publica, the largest publisher of Lithuanian board games, has released a board game "Southern Chronicle", based on the cult writer Rimantas Kmita of the same name.

title: Ketvirtadienio testas: ar atsakysite bent į 8 iš 10 bendrųjų žinių klausimų?
description: Portalas 15min kviečia pasitikrinti jėgas bendrųjų žinių teste. Turėsite atsakyti į 10 įvairių sričių klausimų.
title_translated: Thursday Test: Will you answer at least 8 out of 10 general knowledge questions?
description_translated: The portal 15min invites you to test forces in the general knowledge test. You will need to answer 10 questions from different fields.

title: Namuose Trakų rajone vyras rado moters laikytą ginklą
description: Namuose Trakų rajone vyras rado neteisėtai mirusios moters laikytą ginklą ir šovinius, ketvirtadienį pranešė policija.
title_translated: At home in Trakai district, a man found a female weapon
description_translated: At home in Trakai district, a man found a weapon and ammunition considered to be illegally dead, police said Thursday.

title: Sankt Peterburge užsidegė strateginė elektronikos gamykla
description: Gegužės 29 d. naktį Sankt Peterburge užsidegė strateginė gamykla „Avangard“, kuri specializuojasi mikroelektronikos gamyboje.
title_translated: The strategic electronics factory caught fire in St. Petersburg
description_translated: May 29 At night in St. Petersburg, the strategic factory Avangard, which specializes in microelectronics, was on fire in St. Petersburg.

title: Žiniasklaida: nustatyta, kad Mockaus valdos praplėstos valstybinės žemės sąskaita
description: Valstybinė teritorijų planavimo ir statybos inspekcija (VTPSI) nustatė, kad vieno turtingiausių Lietuvos žmonių, verslininko Dariaus Mockaus valdos Vilniuje praplėstos valstybinės žemės sąskaita, skelbia portalas „Delfi“.
title_translated: Media: It has been found that Mockus' estate expanded by state land expense
description_translated: The State Territorial Planning and Construction Inspectorate (VTPSI) found that one of the richest people in Lithuania, businessman Darius Mockus' estate in Vilnius, was expanded at the expense of state land, according to DELFI.

title: Bronius Medinis: „Klimato kaita reiškiasi kraštutinumais“
description: Gimtasis Rokiškis– Ūkininkai skundžiasi, kad blogus orus jiems siunčiate. – Taip jau išėjo, kad, liūdnai juokaujant, prieš Velykas balandis šilumą „pasiskolino“ iš gegužės, todėl visą gegužę turėjo tęstis kūrenimo sezonas – kone du trečdalius mėnesio vidutinės paros temperatūros buvo žemesnės negu 10 laipsnių šilumos. Vien dėl to, kad balandis paankstino augalų vegetaciją, šalnos labai jai pakentė. [...]Straipsnis Bronius Medinis: „Klimato kaita reiškiasi kraštutinumais“ patalpintas Gimtasis Rokiškis.

description_translated: Native Rokiskis -farmers complain that you send bad weather to them. - It has already come out that, with a sad joke, April "borrowed" the heat from May before Easter, so the burning season had to continue in May - almost two -thirds of the average daily temperature of less than 10 degrees Celsius. Just because April had premature vegetation of plants, the frosts were greatly tolerated by it. [...] Article Bronius Wooden: "Climate Change is manifested by extremes" native Rokiskis.

title: Seimo BFK ketina kviestis LB vadovą dėl interesus galimai supainiojusios Šaučiūnienės
description: Naujienų portalui „15min“ paskelbus, jog pernai iš Lietuvos banko (LB) valdybos pasitraukusi Jurgita Šaučiūnienė tai padarė pripažinus, kad ji galimai supainiojo privačius ir viešus interesus, Seimo Biudžeto ir finansų komitetas (BFK) dėl to ketina kviestis centrinio banko vadovą Gediminą Šimkų.
title_translated: The BFK of the Seimas intends to invite the LB leader on the possibly confused Šaučiūnienė
description_translated: After the news portal "15min" announced that Jurgita Šaučiūnienė, who had left the Bank of Lithuania (LB) last year, did so after acknowledging that she might have confused private and public interests, the Seimas Committee on Budget and Finance (BFK) intends to invite the head of the central bank Gediminas Šimkus.

title: LB vadovas: buvusi valdybos narė Šaučiūnienė netinkamai vykdė pareigas, tai skaudi pamoka
description: Lietuvos banko (LB) valdybos pirmininkas Gediminas Šimkus sako, kad buvusi centrinio banko valdybos narė Jurgita Šaučiūnienė netinkamai vykdė pareigas, o situaciją dėl jos vadina „skaudžia pamoka“.
title_translated: LB CEO: Former Board Member Šaučiūnienė did not properly perform duties, this is a painful lesson
description_translated: Gediminas Šimkus, Chairman of the Board of the Bank of Lithuania (LB), says that former member of the Board of the Central Bank Jurgita Šaučiūnienė did not properly performed his duties and calls the situation a "painful lesson".

title: Raimundas Vaikšnoras: dronų technologijos greitai tobulėja, todėl nebūtina prisipirkti jų iš anksto
description: Lietuvos kariuomenės vadas Raimundas Vaikšnoras sako, kad pirmojo asmens vaizdo principu (angl. first person view, FPV) dronų technologijos tobulėja pernelyg greitai, todėl rengiantis potencialiam konfliktui nebūtina prisipirkti jų iš anksto.
title_translated: Raimundas Walnor: drone technology is rapidly improving so you don't have to buy them in advance
description_translated: The commander of the Lithuanian Armed Forces Raimundas Vaiknoras says that the first -person View (FPV) drone technology is improving too fast, so it is not necessary to buy them in advance when preparing for a potential conflict.

title: Turkija įspėja keleivius: šis veiksmas lėktuve gali brangiai kainuoti
description: Turkijos civilinės aviacijos institucija (CAA) įvedė baudas keleiviams, kurie atsistoja dar neįsijungus saugos diržų ženklui po lėktuvo nusileidimo. Tai įprotis, kuris, kaip teigiama, ne tik trikdo kitus keleivius, bet ir kelia pavojų saugumui.
title_translated: Turkey warns passengers: This action on the plane can cost expensive
description_translated: The Turkish civil aviation authority (CAA) has imposed fines for passengers, which stand up before the seat belt sign has been on after landing. It is a habit that is said to not only interfere with other passengers, but also pose a risk to security.

title: Savaitgalio orai – su trumpais lietumis bei didesne šiluma
description: Gegužės paskutinės dienos pasižymės šiluma bei trumpais lietumis, LRT RADIJUI sako Lietuvos hidrometeorologijos tarnybos sinoptikas Vytautas Sakalauskas.
title_translated: Weekend weather - with short rain and higher heat
description_translated: The last days of May will have warmth and short rain, says Vytautas Sakalauskas, a synoptic of the Lithuanian Hydrometeorological Service, to LRT RADIO.

title: Ką jūsų mėgstami batai pasako apie jūsų asmenybę. Psichologinis testas
description: Psichologai teigia, kad jūsų batai gali daug pasakyti apie mus, ir net mados ekspertai gali nustatyti mūsų asmenybę, pažvelgę į tai, ką mes nešiojame. Juk avalynė yra ne tik mūsų garderobo dalis, bet ir svarbus elementas, kuris gali atspindėti mūsų asmenines savybes ir psichologinę būseną.
title_translated: What your favorite shoes tell about your personality. Psychological test
description_translated: Psychologists say that your shoes can say a lot about us, and even fashion experts can determine our personality by looking at what we wear. After all, footwear is not only part of our wardrobe, but also an important element that can reflect our personal qualities and psychological state.

title: Vaikšnoras: tyrimas dėl Pabradėje žuvusių karių perduotas amerikiečiams
description: Kariuomenės vadas Raimundas Vaikšnoras teigia, kad tyrimas dėl Pabradės poligone žuvusių amerikiečių karių perduotas Jungtinių Amerikos Valstijų (JAV) institucijoms.
title_translated: Walnor: A study on the soldiers who died in Pabrade were handed over to Americans
description_translated: Armed Forces Commander Raimundas Vaišnoras says the investigation into the United States (US) authorities transferred to American troops who died at Pabrade landfill.

title: Orai.lt: bus šilta, bet dažnai palis
description: Šiandien mūsų šalies orus lems anticiklono gūbrys. Dangus bus nepastoviai debesuotas, tik vakarop vakariniame šalies pakraštyje debesų susikaups daugiau ir arčiau jūros vietomis pakrapnos lietus.
title_translated: Orai.lt: will be warm but often rain
description_translated: Today, the weather in our country will be determined by the anticyclone ridge. The sky will be cloudy, only on the western edge of the country, the clouds will accumulate more, and the rain rain is closer to the sea.

title: G. Palucko įmonės direktorius: premjeras verslo veikloje dalyvauja tik kiek leidžia įstatymai
description: Premjerui Gintautui Paluckui iš dalies priklausančios įmonės „Garnis“ direktorius Artūras Lapinskas sako, kad premjeras įmonės veikloje dalyvauja tik kiek jam tai leidžia įstatymai.
title_translated: Director of G. Paluck's company: Prime Minister is involved in business activities only as far as laws allow

description: Pirmos instancijos teismui pernai atmetus Airijos ir Vengrijos oro bendrovių „Ryanair“ ir „Wizz Air“ skundus dėl 2023 metais padidintų rinkliavų Vilniaus oro uoste, ginčas persikėlė į aukščiausios instancijos teismą.
title_translated: Dispute between Ryanair and Wizz Air regarding the fees of Vilnius Airport yet unfinished
description_translated: After the court of first instance dismissed the complaints of Irish and Hungarian airlines Ryanair and Wizz Air about the fees increased at Vilnius Airport last year, the dispute moved to the highest court.

title: Nesėkmingas šuolis per laužą nepilnamečiui baigėsi ligoninėje
description: Policijos pareigūnai aiškinasi, ar nudegimus patyręs nepilnametis išties susižalojo šokdamas per laužą.
title_translated: The unsuccessful leap over the campfire the minor ended in the hospital
description_translated: Police are investigating whether a minor who suffered burns was really injured by jumping through the fire.

title: Orai.lt: ketvirtadienis bus audringas – smarkus lietus, griaustinis, o kai kur gali iškristi ir kruša
description: Ketvirtadienį per Lietuvą slinks frontinė sistema. Dangus bus debesuotas su pragiedruliais, daugelyje rajonų numatomas lietus. Daugiausia vyraus trumpalaikiai lietūs, vietomis gana smarkūs, dažnai lydimi ir perkūnijos griausmo.
title_translated: Orai.lt: Thursday will be stormy - heavy rain, thunder, and in some places can fall out and hail
description_translated: A frontal system will be sought through Lithuania on Thursday. The sky will be cloudy with a cloudy, and in many areas the rain is expected. Most of the rains will prevail, and in some places quite heavy, often accompanied by thunderstorms.

title: Bute Marijampolėje rastas vyro kūnas, sulaikyti trys įtariamieji
description: Bute Marijampolėje trečiadienį rastas mirusio vyro kūnas, sulaikyti trys neblaivūs įtariamieji.
title_translated: A man's body found in the apartment in Marijampolė, detained three suspects
description_translated: In the apartment in Marijampolė, a dead man's body was found on Wednesday and three drunken suspects were detained.

title: Ramiajame vandenyne užsidegė elektromobilius gabenęs laivas
description: Ramiajame vandenyne įsiplieskė ugnis automobilių gabenimo laive „Morning Midas“, kuris iš Kinijos gabeno 3 000 naujų automobilių, iš jų – 800 elektromobilių. Laivo įgula, nesugebėjusi suvaldyti gaisro, buvo evakuota, o visi 22 nariai saugiai perkelti į netoliese buvusį prekybinį laivą.
title_translated: The ship carrying electric vehicles in the Pacific
description_translated: In the Pacific Ocean, the fire on the Morning Mida car was transported, which out of China was transported by 3,000 new cars, including 800 electric cars. The ship's crew, failing to control the fire, was evacuated, and all 22 members were safely transferred to a nearby merchant ship.

title: Kraupūs įvykiai Marijampolėje: bute rastas nužudytas vyras, sulaikyti trys įtariamieji
description: Bute Marijampolėje rastas nužudytas vyras, policija sulaikė nusikaltimu įtariamus tris asmenis. Kaip skelbia Policijos departamentas, trečiadienį, apie 15 val. 30 min., Marijampolėje, Vytauto gatvėje, bute, rastas mirusio vyro (gim. 1972 m.) kūnas. Įtariamieji neblaivūs: (1,83 prom.) moteris (gim. 1971 m.) ir (atsisakė pasitikrinti dėl neblaivumo) vyras (gim. 1970 m.) uždaryti į areštinę, o (1,38 prom.) vyras (gim. 1968 m.) uždarytas į ilgalaikio sulaikymo patalpas.
title_translated: Creepy events in Marijampolė: A killed man found in an apartment, three suspects detained
description_translated: A murdered man was found in the apartment in Marijampolė, and police detained three persons suspected of crime. According to the Police Department, on Wednesday, about 3 p.m. For 30 minutes, the body of a deceased man (born 1972) was found in Marijampolė, Vytauto Street, in the apartment. The suspects are intoxicated: (1.83 prom.) A woman (born 1971) and (refused to test for drunkenness) (born 1970) to close in custody, and (1.38 prom.) A man (born 1968) was closed to long -term detention.

title: Trumpas įvedė kelionių draudimą 12 šalių
description: Motyvuodamas rizika saugumui, JAV prezidentas Donaldas Trumpas trečiadienį įvedė kelionių draudimą 12 šalių. „Aš, kaip prezidentas, turiu imtis veiksmų, kad apsaugočiau Jungtinių Valstijų ir jų žmonių nacionalinį saugumą ir nacionalinius interesus, – proklamacijoje cituojamas D. Trumpas. – Mes atkursime kelionių draudimą, kai kurie žmonės jį vadina D. Trumpo kelionių draudimu, kurį patvirtino Aukščiausiasis Teismas, ir neleisime radikaliems islamo teroristams patekti į mūsų šalį.
title_translated: Brief introduced travel insurance in 12 countries
description_translated: On Wednesday, US President Donald Trump introduced travel insurance in 12 countries. "As a president, I have to take action to protect the national security and national interests of the United States and their people," Trump quoted in proclamation.
